The purposes of this Act are&#8212;
         (a)     to re-enact and modernise the law relating to land tax;
         (b)     to repeal the Land Tax Act 1958;
         (c)     to amend the Taxation Administration Act 1997 so that it
will apply to the administration and enforcement of land tax;
         (d)     to make consequential amendments to other Acts.

